Got my ice bath formula down to a science now !Instead of buying ice everyday , decided to freeze a 24 pack of water bottles and reuse it each morning, and then adding the ice from our fridge everyday too for that added boost.  Down to 39 degrees by the time I get in 🧊 🥶 There’s no way to describe the feeling upon entering and exiting the tub.  A massive rush of energy & dopamine that sustains through the day.  This is incredible for you.  Anti aging type vibe ! I do this every morning right after waking up , then I hit the gym / sauna 💪 🧖‍♂️ Shout out @brandontschannen for putting this quick edit together for me and also @crystal.clouse  for helping me maintain the pool cleanliness needed  #icebath  #coldtherapy #newgoals #health #wellness #coldplunge #cold

Been on a weight loss & overall fitness journey this year, and I’ve finally hit my goal! Down 45 pounds , now it’s time to buckle down and hyperfocus on shred/bulk season. 
My discipline has come a long way since beginning, but I still got many more little sacrifices to make in order to get to that next level 

Not where I want to be , but proud of what I’ve accomplished so far.  I started this entirely for my mental health , and now the physical stuff is just the added benefit.  I know this pic isn’t super impressive , but if you saw me at 240, you know I’m a different man than I was then.

I’m back…🙂
Did ya miss me ? 😜

In all seriousness , this has been one of the roughest weeks of my life…I’ve been at war with myself internally for a while behind the scenes with certain things. 

I won’t go into detail currently here…just know that the good guy in me is winnin, and he isn’t losin this battle ever again 💪

Last night into this morning , I wrote / recorded / mixed / mastered one of my favorite songs I’ve ever made , coming straight out of some of my darkest days…it’ll prolly be a song or two that I drop before I let y’all have this one , bc it means everything to me and I need it fully perfect before I release it 🎶 

Thank you to everyone who reached out to check on me, it means the world fr 🙌

One love , Family ❤️

Celebrating a half a million total plays across all platforms on one of my favorite records of all time 🙌 shout out everyone still keepin “My Life” in rotation through the years ! #hyfe #turnt #bars #mylife #rap #rapper #NF
